OL,7,FAn "abusive and possessive" man has
OL,8,Fbeen sentenced to at least nine years
OL,9,Fin prison for sexual assault, making
OL,10,Fthreats to kill, and assault.
OL,12,FMartin Marko, a 35-year-old from in ,
OL,13,Fpreviously admitted to subjecting his
OL,14,Fvictim to three hours of abuse after
OL,15,Fhe imprisoned her in his flat on 15
OL,16,FAugust 2023.
