OL,7,FBetween 3am and 9am, Marko forced the
OL,8,Fwoman to strip, before he sexually
OL,9,Fassaulted her while brandishing a
OL,10,Fkitchen knife and beating her with a
OL,11,Fshoe. While she was trapped in the
OL,12,Fflat, he choked her, punched her, and
OL,13,Fthrew a bowl of urine at her.
OL,15,FThe attack was caught on CCTV, in
OL,16,Fwhich the woman could be seen begging
OL,17,Ffor her life. On two occasions she
OL,18,Fattempted to escape by climbing out of
OL,19,Fthe first-storey window, only for
OL,20,FMarko to stop her and continue his
OL,21,Fabuse.
