OL,7,FIt was not until after 9am that the
OL,8,Fwoman was finally able to make her
OL,9,Fescape after telling Marko she was
OL,10,Fexpected elsewhere.
OL,12,FShortly after leaving, she called the
OL,13,Fpolice and reported Marko.
OL,15,FOver the next two days, he would go on
OL,16,Fto send 43 texts to the woman both
OL,17,Fapologising for his actions and
OL,18,Fthreatening her to take back her
OL,19,Freport.
