OL,7,FWhen Marko was interviewed by police,
OL,8,Fhe claimed the woman was to blame for
OL,9,Fthe attack, and urged officers to
OL,10,Fcheck the CCTV footage - in which his
OL,11,Fhorrific crimes could clearly be seen.
OL,13,FAfter police recovered the footage, he
OL,14,Fwas charged with sexual assault,
OL,15,Fassault causing actual bodily harm,
OL,16,Fand making threats to kill.
OL,18,FOn 18 March 2024, he appeared at and
OL,19,Fpleaded guilty to all charges.
