OL,7,FIn a statement, the woman said: "The
OL,8,Fwhole matter has affected me on so
OL,9,Fmany levels. Since this happened I've
OL,10,Fnot been able to leave my house. I
OL,11,Ffeel so unsafe. I feel scared of
OL,12,Fwhat's going to happen to me.J"My
OL,13,Fconfidence is completely gone and I
OL,14,Ffeel low about myself. I've lost my
OL,15,Ftrust in everyone.
OL,17,F"From being constantly at home I have
OL,18,Fbegun to feel isolated from my
OL,19,Ffriends. I haven't told anyone what's
OL,20,Fhappened.
