OL,7,F"This has caused me to feel alone in
OL,8,Fthis matter. I'm terrified of him.
OL,9,FMarko has no right to make me feel
OL,10,Flike this. No one has ever made me
OL,11,Ffeel like this before and I feel I
OL,12,Fhave to completely rebuild myself. I
OL,13,Fknow one day I will be completely
OL,14,Fhealed from this situation but it will
OL,15,Ftake time."
OL,17,FDefending Marko, Louise McClusky told
OL,18,Fthe court that he was under the
OL,19,Finfluence of drugs or alcohol at the
OL,20,Ftime of the attack, and had suffered
OL,21,F"a turbulent and difficult childhood".
