OL,7,FShe said: "Children who witness
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse go on to suffer from
OL,9,Fmental health problems and struggle to
OL,10,Fform relationships.
OL,12,F"This defendant clearly proves that
OL,13,Fparticular point. The abusive
OL,14,Fchildhood this defendant had resulted
OL,15,Fin some mental health decline in 2018,
OL,16,Fwhen the defendant began to use
OL,17,Fillicit substances as a way of coping."
