OL,7,FJudge David Aubrey said: "Your victim
OL,8,Fwas petrified and in fear to the
OL,9,Fextent she even contemplated escaping
OL,10,Ffrom your violence, from your threats,
OL,11,Fthrough a window of the flat, which
OL,12,FI'm told was a first floor flat.J"In
OL,13,Fmy judgement, you an abusive and
OL,14,Fpossessive person. You are demanding.
OL,15,FYou were treating your victim as a
OL,16,Fchattel, as an object. You were
OL,17,Fabusive to her. You degraded her.
