OL,7,F"On this particular evening, over a
OL,8,Fprotracted period of time, you were
OL,9,Fdemeaning her, you were controlling
OL,10,Fher, you used violence. You had a
OL,11,Fknife in your hand on a number of
OL,12,Foccasions. You were brandishing that
OL,13,Fknife towards her face. You were
OL,14,Fthreatening her with it. You were
OL,15,Fbeing abusive. You were gesturing
OL,16,Ftowards her in a stabbing motion. On
OL,17,Fone occasion, you threatened to kill
OL,18,Fher."JHe added: "In the aftermath you
OL,19,Fsent to her numerous texts, no less
OL,20,Fthan 43, some of which were of a
OL,21,Fmenacing nature, some of which may
OL,22,Fhave been conciliatory. But your
OL,23,Fintention was to ensure that she
OL,24,Fdidn't speak to the police.
