OL,7,F"Fortunately, while you may be a
OL,8,Fcoward, your victim is a courageous
OL,9,Fwoman. She did make a statement to
OL,10,Fpolice. She didn't retract that
OL,11,Fstatement, none withstanding the
OL,12,Fpressure she was under from you."JHe
OL,13,Fsentenced Marko, of Seaforth Road,
OL,14,FSeaforth, to a 12-year extended
OL,15,Fsentence, ordering him to serve nine
OL,16,Fyears in custody and an extended three
OL,17,Fyears on licence. He also made a
OL,18,Frestraining order banning him from
OL,19,Fcontacting the woman.
